Really?!

45
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,590
Don't worry about it!

46
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:16,200
Please, don't worry about it!

47
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,160
What? What's going on?

48
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:22,330
Okay, well then, good night.

49
00:02:23,230 --> 00:02:24,080
Dad!

50
00:02:24,330 --> 00:02:26,580
Yeah, let's keep it here.

51
00:02:27,740 --> 00:02:29,910
Hey, is that about Chi?

52
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:31,630
