57
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,970
Chi.

58
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:48,140
No! No!

59
00:02:49,890 --> 00:02:50,810
Chi!

60
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:52,860
Let's play?
